{"tid":1184991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】條例列明倘涉國防中央可指令移交　林鄭：影響特首把關權力說法不成立","createTime":"2019-06-04T03:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T03:58:31.000Z","uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0081c30a8a2ca641de5d6f9d01d8c4c360a8ba62","tid":1184991,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:50:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥重申，不會收回有關修例；她表示，數名紀律部隊的首長都曾公開呼籲社會支持條例，「佢哋都係覺得必須要站出嚟講番一啲正義嘅說話」，「我點樣可以，作為行政長官，因為有批評，包括人身嘅批評，而去收番呢項咁重要嘅工作呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190604/s00001/1559616957621/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e5%88%97%e6%98%8e%e5%80%98%e6%b6%89%e5%9c%8b%e9%98%b2%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%ae%e5%8f%af%e6%8c%87%e4%bb%a4%e7%a7%bb%e4%ba%a4-%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad-%e5%bd%b1%e9%9f%bf%e7%89%b9%e9%a6%96%e6%8a%8a%e9%97%9c%e6%ac%8a%e5%8a%9b%e8%aa%aa%e6%b3%95%e4%b8%8d%e6%88%90%e7%ab%8b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190604%2Fs00001%2F1559616957621%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e5%2588%2597%25e6%2598%258e%25e5%2580%2598%25e6%25b6%2589%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%2598%25b2%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25a4%25ae%25e5%258f%25af%25e6%258c%2587%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e4%25ba%25a4-%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad-%25e5%25bd%25b1%25e9%259f%25bf%25e7%2589%25b9%25e9%25a6%2596%25e6%258a%258a%25e9%2597%259c%25e6%25ac%258a%25e5%258a%259b%25e8%25aa%25aa%25e6%25b3%2595%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%25ab%258b&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=576c2f94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190604%2Fs00001%2F1559616957621%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e5%2588%2597%25e6%2